<h3 id="Step-1:-Add-Bot-Connector"><span id="UnifiedAdminGuide-Step1:AddBotConnector"></span>Step 1: Add Bot Connector
 <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
  <copy-clipboard class="anchor-copy-button" value="https://docs.expertflow.com/cx/4.10/unified-admin-guide#Step-1:-Add-Bot-Connector">
   <svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" data-component="icon" class="icon icon-link copy-headline-link-icon">
    <use href="/__theme/b_8ca5a7d7-80f3-41c8-bea7-75cce14ad14f/scroll-sites-help-center-theme/41/icons.svg#link"></use>
   </svg>
  </copy-clipboard>
 </i18n-message></h3>
<p>Make sure that your bot is trained with the essential training data (or is up with the default bot training).&nbsp;</p>
<div data-component="panel" role="note" data-appearance="success">
 <div class="panel-content">
  <p><strong>Tip</strong></p>
  <p>You must have a bot configured in the system to start creating new channels.&nbsp;</p>
  <p>To learn more about Bot-controlled conversations, see <a href="https://expertflow-docs.atlassian.net/wiki/display/CX/Conversation+Studio" data-scope="external" rel="external noreferrer">Conversation Studio - Studio Nodes</a>. To learn more about Bot training, see <a href="/cx-knowledgebase/latest/custom-connector-bot-communication" data-scope="internal">Custom Connector-Bot Communication</a></p>
 </div>
</div>
<div class="theme-block-image">
 <image-lightbox>
  <figure data-component="figure">
   <div class="block-image" style="--width: 600px" data-component="image" data-align="align-center">
    <img src="/__attachments/a_342f3f1e4e2f3cbd886d5f7af6538842dc517f0214859bed3631ae183c6e1c80/add%20bot%20connector.png?cb=e339c22a0d52496804eb5459c7c41b97" alt="add bot connector.png" data-scope="internal" width="623" height="204">
   </div>
   <figcaption>
    <em>Add Bot Connector</em>
   </figcaption>
  </figure>
 </image-lightbox>
</div>
<p>
 <br>
</p>
<p style="--text-align: center">
 <br>
</p>
<p>Expand the <strong>Rasa</strong> type and click, <strong>Add Bot&nbsp;</strong>to add the default controller bot.</p>
<div class="theme-table" style="--width: 1800px;">
 <table-expand>
  <scroll-shadow>
