        </th>
        <th>
         <p><strong>Description</strong></p>
        </th>
       </tr>
       <tr>
        <th>
         <p><strong>Bot Name</strong></p>
        </th>
        <td>
         <p>Specify a name to be given to the bot.&nbsp;</p>
        </td>
