  <p><span style="--color: #202124">By default, Rasa Bot is supported as the controller bot with default bot training. </span><span style="--color: #202124"><em>&lt;</em></span><span style="--color: #f00"><em>give a link to the bot training</em></span><span style="--color: #202124"><em>&gt;</em></span><span style="--color: #202124">&nbsp;</span></p>
  <p><span style="--color: #202124">If a Bot Connector is being used with a Channel or anywhere else, the system does not allow to delete of such a Bot until this association is removed.</span></p>
