<h3 id="Reviewing-Conversations"><span id="UnifiedAdminGuide-ReviewingConversations"></span>Reviewing Conversations
 <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
  <copy-clipboard class="anchor-copy-button" value="https://docs.expertflow.com/cx/4.10/unified-admin-guide#Reviewing-Conversations">
   <svg role="img" aria-hidden="true" data-component="icon" class="icon icon-link copy-headline-link-icon">
    <use href="/__theme/b_8ca5a7d7-80f3-41c8-bea7-75cce14ad14f/scroll-sites-help-center-theme/41/icons.svg#link"></use>
   </svg>
  </copy-clipboard>
 </i18n-message></h3>
<ul>
 <li>
  <p>Click on a conversation to open its detailed view.</p>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p>The conversation view displays:</p>
  <ul>
   <li>
    <p>A chronological history of messages or call records.</p>
   </li>
   <li>
    <p>Interaction details, such as client responses, agent replies, and system actions.</p>
   </li>
  </ul>
 </li>
 <li>
  <p><strong>Actions:</strong></p>
  <ul>
   <li>
    <p>Assign: Opens the Assign Panel where you can:</p>
    <ul>
     <li>
      <p>Select an evaluator.</p>
     </li>
     <li>
      <p>Assign an agent for review.</p>
     </li>
     <li>
      <p>Choose a questionnaire.</p>
     </li>
     <li>
      <p>Set a due date and reminders.</p>
     </li>
     <li>
      <p>Confirm by clicking Assign.</p>
     </li>
    </ul>
   </li>
   <li>
    <p>Review: Opens the Review Panel where you can:</p>
    <ul>
     <li>
      <p>Select an agent to review.</p>
     </li>
     <li>
      <p>Choose a questionnaire for the evaluation.</p>
     </li>
     <li>
      <p>Click Start Review to begin the process.</p>
     </li>
    </ul>
   </li>
   <li>
    <p><strong>Viewing Conversation Types</strong></p>
    <ul>
     <li>
      <p>Use the dropdown at the top-right to filter by:</p>
      <ul>
       <li>
        <p><strong>All:</strong> Displays both chat and voice conversations.</p>
       </li>
       <li>
        <p><strong>Chat:</strong> Shows only chat-based interactions.</p>
       </li>
       <li>
        <p><strong>Voice:</strong> Displays voice calls.</p>
       </li>
      </ul>
     </li>
    </ul>
   </li>
  </ul>
 </li>
</ul>
